name: Botivo Non-Alcoholic Aperitivo
description: Bittersweet aperitivo bursting with bright citrus and fresh herbal notes

name: Guinness Zero Draught 440ml Cans
description:
Aroma: Sweet smelling with a coffee and malty nose.
Flavour: Perfect balance of bitter and sweet with malt and roast characters.
Palate: Smooth, creamy and balanced.

name: Birra Moretti Zero 330ml
description:
It is a Blonde beer of low fermentation, obtained by a wise mixture of water, barley malt and selected hop flowers.
It has an intense aroma, is of medium corps and has a balanced and aromatic taste. Light and pleasant to drink.

name: Lucky Saint 330ml
description: Lucky Saint is a 0.5% Superior Unfiltered Lager made with just four natural ingredients - Pilsner Malt, Hallertau Hops, Bavarian Spring Water and single-use yeast. We leave our beer unfiltered for maximum flavour, without the alcohol. 53 calories per bottle and vegan.

name: Wild Idol Non-Alcoholic Sparkling Rose
description: Expect elegant floral aromas, abundant red fruit and crisp green apple flavours, zesty hints of gooseberry, rhubarb and grapefruit – before a long and lively finish, rich with hints of vanilla and toasted almond.

name: McGuigan Zero Shiraz
description: Subtle spice and vanilla notes complimented by plum and forest berry aromas. This shiraz has flavours of sweet blackcurrants and a round finish. Pairs perfectly with a chocolate dessert, a BBQ but equally delicious on its own

name: Peroni 0.0% 330ml
description: The newest addition to the family, Peroni Libera 0.0% delivers a crisp and refreshing taste, with a delicate fruity aroma. First brewed with exclusive Nostrano dell'Isola maize, with a dedicated yeast strain then added without producing alcohol. This gives Peroni Libera 0.0% its signature hoppy characteristics and smooth finish.

name: Wild Idol Non-Alcoholic Sparkling Rose Half Bottle
description: Expect elegant floral aromas, abundant red fruit and crisp green apple flavours, zesty hints of gooseberry, rhubarb and grapefruit – before a long and lively finish, rich with hints of vanilla and toasted almond.

name: Heineken 0.0 Alcohol Free Beer 330ml
description:
Our master brewers started from zero and spent years exploring, brewing and tasting before they finally created a recipe defined by its refreshing fruity notes and soft malty body - perfectly balanced with only 69 calories.
Heineken 0.0 is a refreshing alcohol free beer characterised by fruity and fresh malt notes and a lightbody.

name: Estrella Galicia Low Alcohol 330ml
description:
Flavour:
It has a sharp and sturdy bitterness on the palate, which adds a very dry hint to this beer. Aroma:
Its aroma reminds us of the malts used in the production of beer wort, with subtle floral and hoppy notes.

name: Lyre's Dry London Spirit
description: Firm flavours with juniper and citrus. Earthy notes fill the mid-palate which has lovely vinous qualities. The pepperberry adds warmth and delivers a generous, dry finish.

name: Old Mout Low Alcohol Berries & Cherries 500ml
description:
Aroma: Summery burst of fruits of the forest.
Taste: A special blend of strawberry and raspberry with notes of blueberry. Finished off with a refreshing burst of juicy apple.

name: Sharp's Doom Bar Zero
description: Doom Bar Zero is a perfectly balanced beer combining subtle yet complex flavours, Doom Bar Zero is both satisfying and deliciously moreish.

name: Estrella Damm 0% ( Free Damm ) Alcohol Free Beer 20L Keg
description: Free Damm Lager is brewed in Barcelona using the same ingredients we use to brew a premium, alcoholic beer. An advanced vacuum, distillation technique means the alcohol is removed but the refreshing beer flavour of Free Damm is kept.

name: McGuigan Zero Chardonnay
description: Attractive aromas of white peach combine with subtle influences of vanilla and oak. The palate is intensely driven by stone fruit and honey melon flavours with the toasty oak ensuring a rounded, generous finish.

name: Everleaf Forest
description:
Aroma: Heady vetiver and orange blossom with notes of earthy orris root and warm vanilla.
Taste: Bold and vibrant with layers of citrus, bark, spices, bittersweet roots and savoury saffron.
Finish: Long and complex, with Everleaf’s signature mouthfeel holding on to the myriad of flavours lengthened with moreish bitter gentian root.

name: Vita Libera Primitivo
description: Vita Libera is produced with quality Primitivo wine, carefully selected for having the perfect attributes to be dealcoholized with the best result. Bright ruby in colour. Vita Libera Primitivo has a pronounced fruity bouquet reminiscent of crispy red fruits, such as berries. The palate is well-balanced, smooth with a persistent finish.

name: Asahi 0.0% 330ml
description: Inspired by dry sake, we invented the world’s first super dry beer. We named it Asahi Super Dry and changed the world of beer forever. A crisp and clean super dry taste that’s like no other and that goes beyond the typical beer taste

name: Bristol Beer Clear Head Alchohol Free IPA 440ml
description:
Alcohol-free IPA | Mosaic | Citra. Embracing Bristol Beer Factory’s craft beer energy Clear Head brings the best in hop and body to the Alcohol-Free world. Citra & Mosaic hops swing in with big US citrus notes and lactose adds the IPA body. 5% of total sales go directly to TALK CLUB, a Bristol U.K born charity helping create a sustainable, positive mental health community.
CLEAR HEAD is a beer for good.

name: Bolle Sparkling Rose
description: An expressive bouquet of white strawberry, red berries, blackcurrant, violet, and a hint of fresh herbs. It is dry and fresh on the palate with delicate bubbles and a touch of minerality. Flavours include sweet strawberry, blackcurrant, and cherry, with light savoury herbal notes complementing the fruitiness. The finish is long and lingering.
